      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fazhe ee-\nfahrotees/ un fazzija: Kas dohs\nman Uhdeni dsert no tahe Ak-\nkas/ kas eekſch Betlemes Wahr-\ntun irr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad lausahs tee trihs zaur\nto Wilistexu Lehgeri/ un finehle\nUhdeni no Betlemes Akkas/ kas\nWahrtis bija/ un nehme/ un at-\nneffe to pee Dahwida. Bet Dah-\nwids to ne gribbeja dsert/ bet is-\nlehje to preekſch ta KUNGA/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija : Lai man\nDeews no ta paſarga/ ka es to\nbuhtu darrijs/ un scho Wihru Af-\nfini dsehrts/ jo tee irr ar fawas\nDsihwibas likstu to atneffufschi/\nun wiꞥſch ne gribbeja to dsert.\nScho darrija fchee trihs Warre-\nnee.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abisajus Joaba Brah-\nlis bija arridsan par Wirfneefu\npahr trim/ un tas pazehle fa-\nwn Schkehpu/ un nokawe trihs-\nfimts. Un tam btja arri Sla-\nwa starp trim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Starp teem trim btja\nwiꞥſch jo augsts ne ka tee diwi/\nun wiꞥſch bija teem par Wirfnee-\nfu/ bet wiꞥſch ne panahze tohs\ntrihs ( pirrnajus ).\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Benajus Jojada Dehis\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weena stipra Wihra Dehis/ kas\nleetus Darbus darrijs no Kab-\nzeëles/ tas kawe divi stiprus\nMoabitexu Lauwas/ un nogahje\narridsan/ uu kawe weenu Lau-\nwu pascha Allā Sneega Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch nokawe arridsan\nweenu Egiptes Wihru/ weenu\ntahdu Wihru/ kas peezas Oh-\nlechts garſch bija/ un tam Egipte-\nram bija weens Schkebps Roh-\nkā/ ka weena Reestawa/bet tchis\nnogahje pee ta ar weenu Sisli/\nnn isrnhwe to Schkehpu no ta\nEgiptea Rohkas/ un nokawe to\nar winna pascha Schkehpu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Scho darrija Benajus\nJojada Dehis/ un schis bija fla-\nwehts starp trim Warreneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch bija tas aug-\nstakajs starp trihsdefiniteem/ bet\nwiꞥſch ne panahze tohs trihs\n(pirrnajus). Un Dahwids ee-\nzehle to pahr taween Pils Karra-\nWihreem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta Karra-Speka\nWarrenee bija: Asaēts/ Joaba\nBrahlis. Elanans/ Dodus\nDehis no Betlemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sanots/ tas Aroriteris,\nEelez/ tas Pelonntteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irus/ Efesa Dehis tas\nTekötteris. Abtēsers/ tas Air-\ntotiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sibekajus/ tas Usattite-\nris. Ilajus/ tas Akōiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Makarajus/ tas Neto-\nwatiteris. Eeleds/ Baēnus\nDehis/ tas Netowatiteris.\n"
